sql_query.sql: SELECT "apps".* FROM "apps" INNER JOIN "orgs" ON ("orgs"."id" = "apps"."org_id") WHERE (("public" IS TRUE) AND ("apps"."slug" = 'appland') AND ("orgs"."slug" = 'default')) LIMIT 1

SELECT "apps".* FROM "apps" INNER JOIN "orgs" ON ("orgs"."id" = "apps"."org_id") INNER JOIN "users" ON ("users"."id" = "orgs"."owner_id") WHERE (("public" IS TRUE) AND ("apps"."slug" = 'appland') AND ("users"."login" = 'default')) LIMIT 1
